<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.8">
<l>pācitūrt tukkiṭanta pārmakaṭku paṇṭorunāḷ</l>
<l>mācuṭampil nīrvāra māṉamilāp paṉṟiyām</l>
<l>tēcuṭaiya tēvar tiruvaraṅkac celvaṉār</l>
<l>pēci yiruppaṉakaḷ pērkkavum pērāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The words spoken by</l>
<l>the Wealthy Man from Śrīraṅgam, the lustrous God,</l>
<l>—who became a shameless boar with [muddy] water dripping from [His] dirty body</l>
<l>on a day in the past, for the sake of the Earth Lady who lay covered with moss—</l>
<l>will not be moved [from my heart] even when tried.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
